# Setup Environment

```bash
# Install dependencies using uv (no need to manually create venv)
uv sync
```

# Start LangGraph Agent

From root directory:

```bash
uv run python -m agents.app
```

# Start a2a Inspector

Frontend:

```bash
cd a2a-inspector/frontend && npm run build -- --watch
```

Backend:

```bash
cd a2a-inspector/backend && uv run app.py
```

# Start Agent Chat UI

```bash
cd demo/ui && uv run main.py
```

# Endpoint URLs

## LangGraph Currency Agent

```text
http://localhost:10000
```

## a2a Inspector

```text
http://127.0.0.1:5001
```

## Agent Chat UI

```text
http://0.0.0.0:12000/
```